&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FigFile:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The FigFile Content team manages the infrastructure that supports file and asset operations. As the Engineering Manager, you will be instrumental in shaping the future of Figma&#39;s file management capabilities, ensuring that our systems are secure, efficient, and scalable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role impacts both our internal processes and the experience of millions of users worldwide. You will collaborate closely with product, design, and engineering teams to integrate new features and optimize existing systems, building and extending our infrastructure to support a diverse set of products and features. The role presents opportunities to tackle challenges such as expanding data locality, implementing enterprise-grade encryption solutions, and enhancing content management systems, all of which are vital to Figma&#39;s growth and success in the competitive design software landscape.&lt;/li&gt;
